eft, and on the 4tb-hdd about 30gb.\r\ni tried to set quota to unlimited, to 6tb, and to the exact amount of physical available space - nothing changes\r\nhowever - owncloud is soooo great - go on guys!!\r\n--\r\nsystem: opensuse tumbleweed x64, ui shown on firefox kde, db is sql-lite."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/18005144","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2337#issuecomment-18005144","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2337","id":18005144,"user":{"login":"hauskins","id":3869468,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/949223b5cc65a6e69cf91296be038daa?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fc6972b45966ea821ced746af8a27ec03.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"949223b5cc65a6e69cf91296be038daa","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins","html_url":"https://github.com/hauskins","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hauskins/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-05-16t14:39:26z","updated_at":"2013-05-16t14:39:26z","body":"so this patch to local.php  #2318 fixes the file size too large and upload button showing b, which did not allow anything uploaded via the web interface.  but you still get the top banner message saying you have no space left unless you set the quota to something besides unlimited.  \r\n\r\nso at the moment my setup is working.  ;-)"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/i