tps://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2337#issuecomment-22342175","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2337","id":22342175,"user":{"login":"tomtomme","id":4428185,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/34afd804e63706527723330d33beea7a?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f04b2fa845da43f0f670c1d5bb304c205.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"34afd804e63706527723330d33beea7a","url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme","html_url":"https://github.com/tomtomme","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/tomtomme/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-08t17:59:40z","updated_at":"2013-08-08t17:59:40z","body":"this is inactive because no one does something about it ... but its still there with 5.0.9\r\n\r\n### expected behaviour\r\ncalculate disk space right from disks that are present\r\n\r\n### actual behaviour\r\nowncloud does not recognize if an (usb)-hdd is not there anymore and calculates wrong sizes of \"disk space used\" and \"disk space available\". then it complains about no disk space left even if there is still disk space left on the other disks. error message see screenshot above...\r\n\r\n### steps to reproduce\r\n1. connect a external usb-hdd to your pc\r\n2. add this as external storage via the admin-configuration page\r\n3. remove the drive from your pc, but let the configuration stay the same\r\n4. owncloud does not recognize that the hdd is not there anymore and calculates wrong sizes of disk space used and disk space available\r\n5. it starts complaining...\r\n6. remove the external storage from configuration, now it stops complaining\r\n7. but then it shows only available space left on /. the space left on the other disk mounted on /home/name/data is ignored.\r\n\r\n### server configuration\r\noperating system:\r\nopensuse tumbleweed x64\r\nweb server: \r\napache/2.2.22\r\ndatabase:\r\nsqlite version 2.8.17\r\nphp version:\r\nphp 5.3.17 (cli)\r\nowncloud version:\r\n5.0.9\r\n### client configuration\r\nbrowser:\r\nmozilla firefox 22.0 or dolphin (webdav)\r\noperating system:\r\nserver and client are the same machine at the moment for testing until everything works\r\n\r\n```\r\ndf -h\r\ndateisystem    grã¶ãÿe benutzt verf. verw% eingehã¤ngt auf\r\n--------------\r\n/dev/sda1       1,4t    1,3t   19g   99% /home/thomas/1data\r\n/dev/sdb1        38g     28g  8,2g   78% /\r\n---------------------\r\ndevtmpfs        3,9g    4,0k  3,9g    1% /dev\r\ntmpfs           4,0g    1,6m  4,0g    1% /dev/shm\r\ntmpfs           4,0g    964k  4,0g    1% /run\r\ntmpfs           4,0g       0  4,0g    0% /sys/fs/cgroup\r\ntmpfs           4,0g    5,2m  4,0g    1% /tmp\r\ntmpfs           4,0g    964k  4,0g    1% /var/run\r\ntmpfs           4,0g    964k  4,0g    1% /var/lock\r\n```\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22348393","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2337#issuecomment-22348393","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2337","id":22348393,"user":{"login":"jancborchardt","id":925062,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/2fd3f4d5d762955e5b603794a888fa97?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f84ec51f9ceed468217d4e13abf78da9c.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"2fd3f4d5d762955e5b603794a888fa97","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt","html_url":"https://github.com/jancborchardt","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/follo